Desert Sage Infusion[dnd-info]=Enjoy this soothing infusion as a calming drink or use it as a base for other recipes.;*Ingredients*;-1 tablespoon dried Desert Sage leaves;-1 cup boiling water;*Instructions*;-Place the dried Desert Sage leaves in a teapot or a heatproof container.;-Pour boiling water over the leaves.;-Cover and let it steep for about 10 minutes.;-Strain the infusion into a cup.;-Optionally, you can add a teaspoon of honey or lemon juice for taste.
